队在积极对接了解大模型，这是好的信号。ChatGPT和AI大模型，下一个时代的跳板？| 502回顾"},"attached_info":"ClUIvb69nOqa4fkGEAMaCDkxNDYyMDE4IL3K3Z4GMAE4nwxAHXIJNTgxMzExNDkxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"61 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-1da0695d0cd66e16c21c4589261c1d20_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"30_1677482069.584585","card_id":"Q_586425548","target":{"id":586425548,"title":"一个人怎样才能愿意改变自己?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/586425548","type":"question","created":1677446814,"answer_count":42,"follower_count":62,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[199,7129,35034],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"当一个处于人生低谷，面临巨大困难，如何快速战胜自己?"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ivb69nOqa4fkGEAMaCDkyNTk4NDgwIJ6d758GMAA4PkAecgk1ODY0MjU1NDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"60 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"31_1677482069.585078","card_id":"Q_584235649","target":{"id":584235649,"title":"哪款咖啡机最适合一个人独居使用？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/584235649","type":"question","created":1676456398,"answer_count":24,"follower_count":61,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[307,3519,12278,106840,153736],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我是一位咖啡爱好者，也是一人独居的人，喜欢在家里自己冲咖啡。但是我觉得现在手冲实在是太麻烦了，所以想买一台咖啡机。但是市面上有各种各样的咖啡机，不知道哪一款适合我这种情况，希望能得到一些指导。"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ivb69nOqa4fkGEAMaCDkyMTEyMDM5IM7jsp8GMAI4PUAfcgk1ODQyMzU2NDl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-27be3ed520b137faf6e55bd12af3cde